<p>May your life be blessed with joy, love and miracles!</p>
<p>希望你的生活里充满了欢乐、关爱和奇迹。</p>
<p>God bless you and your family at Thanksgiving and always!</p>
<p>上帝会保佑你和你的家人!</p>
<p>Have a FULL Thanksgiving day!</p>
<p>感恩节快乐!好好吃一顿吧!</p>
<p>Joy and fun, wish fulfillment and blessing, come to your home this Thanksgiving!</p>
<p>感恩节里尽情享受快乐吧!</p>
<p>Wish you a very special Thanksgiving Day for you and your family.</p>
<p>愿你们有一个特别的感恩节。</p>
<p>I am so grateful that I have you all with me on this Thanksgiving Day.</p>
<p>非常感谢有你们和我在一起。</p>
<p>Season's greetings to you all straight from our hearts.</p>
<p>感恩节里献上最诚挚的祝福。</p>
<p>From all of us to all of you at Thanksgiving.</p>
<p>请接受我们诚挚的祝福：祝你们感恩节快乐!</p>
